        "title": "A docs root is the unit of authority",
        "tone": "decision"
      },
      "text": [
        {
          "insert": "DocsStore accepts paths relative to one docs root. It has no project identifier, project record, or host database connection. A host must resolve its own workspace, project, or command-line selection to a docs root before entering the package."
        }
      ],
      "children": []
